s/2026/01/SideQuested-06-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/SideQuested-06-80x80.webp 80w, https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/SideQuested-06-768x768.webp 768w, https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/SideQuested-06.webp 1168w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></div></div>
<p>You can still preorder your copy! <a href="https://sidequested.com/book/#preorder">Here are the links</a> to every online store we’ve found, but you can also request it at your local bookstore! Every preorder counts towards our publishing day launch stats, which have a ridiculous impact in the publishing industry! If we can show that <strong>Side Quested Book 1 </strong>has strong sales data, we could bring the entire series to print!</p>
<div class="su-divider su-divider-style-dotted" style="margin:5px 0;border-width:2px;border-color:#999999"></div>
<h3>CLAIM YOUR PRIZE!</h3>
<p>If you’ve already preordered the first book, Andrews McMeel Universal, our wonderful Publisher, has a digital reward for you! <strong><a href="https://site.andrewsmcmeel.com/sidequested-pre-order-incentive" target="_blank">A high-resolution Movie Poster of Side Quested is available here!</a></strong> Just enter your name and email and the download will be sent directly to your account.</p>
<p><a href="http://https://site.andrewsmcmeel.com/sidequested-pre-order-incentive" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/AMU-preorderBanner1.webp" alt="" width="1024" height="512" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3269" srcset="https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/AMU-preorderBanner1.webp 1024w, https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/AMU-preorderBanner1-300x150.webp 300w, https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/AMU-preorderBanner1-768x384.webp 768w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></p>
<p>The incentive promo is available until book launch! (12:00 CST on 17 March, 2026)</p>
<div class="su-divider su-divider-style-dotted" style="margin:5px 0;border-width:2px;border-color:#999999"></div>
<h3>PROMO VIDEO</h3>
<p>We’ve also made this incredible trailer for the first book! Written by KB, edited by Ale, and narrated by the one and only <strong><a href="https://bsky.app/profile/itsdanicarr.bsky.social" target="_blank">Dani Carr</a></strong> (who&#8217;s now also a fellow <a href="https://thewitchwolf.org/" target="_blank">webcomic creator!</a>), we’re hoping this appeals to new and old readers alike.  </p>
<div class="su-youtube su-u-responsive-media-yes"><iframe width="400" height="600" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cchL6tKChhM?" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture" title="Side Quested Book 1 Promo Video"></iframe></div>
<p>We&#8217;ll be posting it on all of our social media channels. If you’re inclined to share, this would be amazing and appreciated!</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DU0eX6HE89e/" target="_blank">Instagram</a> | <a href="https://youtu.be/cchL6tKChhM" target="_blank">Youtube</a> | <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/alepresser.com/post/3meyfgyqiuc2u" target="_blank">BlueSky</a> | <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@alepresser/video/7607452378513739010" target="_blank">TikTok</a> | <a href="https://mastodon.art/@AlePresser/116080535890320324" target="_blank">Mastodon</a> | <a href="https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/85jrodbymb0kzleocw1g9/SQB1.mp4?rlkey=z1xtgubt8lxwxdr7cs5rlf7he&#038;dl=0" target="_blank">Download and share!</a></strong></p>
<div class="su-divider su-divider-style-dotted" style="margin:5px 0;border-width:2px;border-color:#999999"></div>
<h3>NEW MERCH SHOP</h3>
<p>To celebrate book launch, we&#8217;re also launching our new merch store at <a href="https://www.gossipbirdbooks.com/" target="_blank">gossipbirdbooks.com</a>! </p>
<p><a href="https://www.gossipbirdbooks.com/" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/newshopbanner.webp" alt="" width="945" height="459" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3270" srcset="https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/newshopbanner.webp 945w, https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/newshopbanner-300x146.webp 300w, https://sidequested.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/newshopbanner-768x373.webp 768w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 945px) 100vw, 945px" /></a></p>
<p>The new store has both digital and physical products, and as <strong>SIDE QUESTED</strong> has a global readership, we’ve made sure the store offers worldwide shipping. We&#8217;re launching with just a couple of products, but more are coming soon!</p>
<div class="su-divider su-divider-style-dotted" style="margin:5px 0;border-width:2px;border-color:#999999"></div>
<h3>REVIEWS</h3>
<p>Could you help us track reviews? Book reviews come from everywhere these days, and it’s hard to catch them all! We&#8217;re trying to Pokémon all of them and are <a href="https://sidequested.com/book/#reviews">listing them here on our main website</a>, but if you come across a new one, please let us know!</p>
<div class="su-divider su-divider-style-dotted" style="margin:5px 0;border-width:2px;border-color:#999999"></div>
<h3>YOU ARE THE BEST!</h3>
<p>Yes, you are. <strong>Side Quested Book 1 </strong>is a huge milestone and we wouldn’t have reached it without you. We&#8217;re only able to keep working because of your support. Thank you, <em>thank you, <strong>thank you!</strong></em></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://sidequested.com/countdown-to-book-launch/">Countdown to Book Launch!</a> appeared first on <a href="https://sidequested.com">Side Quested Webcomic</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
